            "type": "text",
            "text": "F16",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " variant costing $0.0015 per image for the first 10,000 requests monthly, dropping to $0.0012 beyond that. Additional costs may apply for premium features like table extraction or handwriting specialization. For a production system processing 1 million images monthly, expect a base cost of $1,200, plus potential overages for high-resolution images."
          }
        ]
      },
