      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Nanonets OCR S excels in handwritten text recognition, outperforming Google Vision by 2.5% WER on such inputs. However, for purely printed text at scale, Tesseract may be more cost-effective if you can manage infrastructure. Refer to the "
          },
          {
            "type": "a",
            "url": "https://cloud.google.com/vision/pricing",
            "title": null,
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
